title: 2016 Billboard Latin Music Awards Photos: Red Carpet & More!
text:
065 J Balvin Onstage with Fuego 
J Balvin is a top finalist for the 2017 Billboard Latin Music Awards taking place April 27 in Miami. The chart-topping artist is up for artist of the year and Latin Rhythm Song of the year with "Bobo." In celebration of the finalists announced today (Feb. 7), below check out standout moments and performances from last year's awards ceremony. John Parra/Telemundo
